@startuml FE17_GetFrequencyAnalytics_Sequence
title FE17 - Get Frequency Analytics (FeatG46) - Consumed by FE-16

actor User
participant UI
participant GetFrequencyAnalyticsEndpoint
participant MediatR
participant GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler
participant Cache
participant FloodAnalyticsFrequencyRepository
database Database

User -> UI: 1. View flood history chart
UI -> GetFrequencyAnalyticsEndpoint: 2. GET /api/v1/analytics/frequency?areaId=...&startDate=...&endDate=...&bucketType=day
activate GetFrequencyAnalyticsEndpoint
GetFrequencyAnalyticsEndpoint -> MediatR: 3. Send(GetFrequencyAnalyticsRequest)
activate MediatR
MediatR -> GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler: 4. Handle(request)
activate GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler

GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler -> GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler: 5. BuildCacheKey(areaId, startDate, endDate, bucketType)
activate GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler

GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler -> Cache: 6. GetFromCache(cacheKey)
activate Cache
alt [Cache Hit]
    Cache --> GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler: 7. Cached data
    GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler --> MediatR: 8. Response (from cache)
else [Cache Miss]
    Cache --> GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler: 9. null
    deactivate Cache
    
    GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler -> FloodAnalyticsFrequencyRepository: 10. GetByAreaAndPeriod(areaId, startDate, endDate, bucketType)
    activate FloodAnalyticsFrequencyRepository
    FloodAnalyticsFrequencyRepository -> Database: 11. SELECT * FROM flood_analytics_frequency WHERE area_id = ? AND time_bucket BETWEEN ? AND ? AND bucket_type = ? ORDER BY time_bucket
    Database --> FloodAnalyticsFrequencyRepository: 12. List<FloodAnalyticsFrequency>
    FloodAnalyticsFrequencyRepository --> GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler: 13. List<FloodAnalyticsFrequency>
    deactivate FloodAnalyticsFrequencyRepository
    
    GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler -> GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler: 14. MapToDto(entities)
    activate GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler
    
    GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler -> Cache: 15. SetCache(cacheKey, data, TTL: 1 hour)
    activate Cache
    Cache --> GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler: 16. Cached
    deactivate Cache
    
    GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler --> MediatR: 17. Response {success: true, data}
    deactivate GetFrequencyAnalyticsHandler
end

MediatR --> GetFrequencyAnalyticsEndpoint: 18. Response
deactivate MediatR
GetFrequencyAnalyticsEndpoint --> UI: 19. HTTP 200 OK (FrequencyAnalyticsDto)
deactivate GetFrequencyAnalyticsEndpoint
UI --> User: 20. Display flood frequency chart

@enduml

